to the oral center of the
scene and preserving it as well

00:14:14.510 --> 00:14:17.140
as marry it to the visual.

00:14:17.140 --> 00:14:20.740
His career has spanned
live network television

00:14:20.740 --> 00:14:23.040
with a list too numerous
to announce.

00:14:23.040 --> 00:14:28.120
If you picked it up in
the back, oh my goodness.

00:14:30.040 --> 00:14:39.460
Including the Watergate hearing,
radio production, theater,

00:14:39.460 --> 00:14:43.020
multitrack recording,
film documentary,

00:14:43.020 --> 00:14:45.870
and feature film
sound recordings.

00:14:45.870 --> 00:14:50.380
His quest for perfection has
garnered him two Academy Awards

00:14:50.380 --> 00:14:54.010
in the category sound
for the movies "Glory"

00:14:54.010 --> 00:14:55.480
and "Dances With Wolves."

00:14:55.480 --> 00:14:59.620
And two primetime Emmys for
the documentaries "Terrorists

00:14:59.620 --> 00:15:01.760
on Trial, the United States

00:15:01.760 --> 00:15:06.070
Versus Salim Ajami,"
and "12 angry men."

00:15:06.070 --> 00:15:12.510
He is the first African-American
multi-Academy Award winner.

00:15:12.510 --> 00:15:19.950
[ Applause ]

00:15:19.950 --> 00:15:23.420
Mr. Williams of his many years
of experience in the industry

00:15:23.420 --> 00:15:26.600
and apply those blessings
to produce in a career.

00:15:26.600 --> 00:15:29.790
He is very passionate about.

00:15:29.790 --> 00:15:34.090
He has worked jointly with Isis
Films director Bobby Holland

00:15:34.090 --> 00:15:38.780
on videos, commercials and
behind the scenes documentaries.

00:15:38.780 --> 00:15:40.080
This seasoned veteran

00:15:40.080 --> 00:15:42.700
of the motion picture
world has spent more

00:15:42.700 --> 00:15:46.850
than 30 years applying his
trade on all but two continents

00:15:46.850 --> 00:15:51.170
and in all 4 of the 50 states.

00:15:51.170 --> 00:15:54.270
His credo has been
getting the most

00:15:54.270 --> 00:15:57.610
with the least clutter
and confusion.

00:15:57.610 --> 00:16:00.810
In 2002, Williams
