and they're like ah.

00:54:51.060 --> 00:54:53.980
And you know, they may have
the best of intentions.

00:54:53.980 --> 00:54:56.480
A lot of those guys I worked
with at WMAL radio said man,

00:54:56.480 --> 00:54:57.780
you're a fool if you
think you're going

00:54:57.780 --> 00:55:00.570
to get any work in Los Angeles.

00:55:00.570 --> 00:55:02.210
Okay, well I'm that
kind of fool.

00:55:02.210 --> 00:55:07.230
I got 90 days to find out
[laughter] whether your version

00:55:07.230 --> 00:55:09.820
of me is right, or my
version of me is right.

00:55:09.820 --> 00:55:11.500
But the nay-sayers
are important,

00:55:11.500 --> 00:55:14.650
because if they can talk you
out of pursuing your dream,

00:55:14.650 --> 00:55:17.260
you weren't going
to do it anyway.

00:55:17.260 --> 00:55:21.340
Let me repeat that, you
weren't going to do it anyway.

00:55:21.340 --> 00:55:23.550
Because even if everything
works out fine,

00:55:23.550 --> 00:55:26.150
there's still going
to be resistance.

00:55:26.150 --> 00:55:29.580
You still have to be the best,
which means that you've got

00:55:29.580 --> 00:55:31.390
to put in the extra hours,
you've got to be competitive,

00:55:31.390 --> 00:55:33.590
you've got to do all this new
work to learn this new field.

00:55:33.590 --> 00:55:37.600
So, that's with nothing
else interfering with that.

00:55:37.600 --> 00:55:40.670
And of course, when
I went to LA in '79,

00:55:40.670 --> 00:55:43.590
it was not an original idea.

00:55:43.590 --> 00:55:45.630
So, there's a long line of
people that get off the plane

00:55:45.630 --> 00:55:48.570
at LAX thinking they're going
to do something in showbusiness.

00:55:48.570 --> 00:55:52.940
So, just look at that
line, and say okay well,

00:55:52.940 --> 00:55:56.750
be here for a little while,
but that's how we vet you,

00:55:56.750 --> 00:55:58.340
that's how we get
rid of the people

00:55:58.340 --> 00:56:00.640
who are really not serious.

00:56:00.640 --> 00:56:02.270
You know, if you get a
law degree, you still have

00:56:02.270 --> 00:56:04.490
