You get a medical degree,

00:56:08.020 --> 00:56:09.500
you have to pass the state
boards before you can start

00:56:09.500 --> 00:56:13.630
chopping people up,
that's a vetting process.

00:56:13.630 --> 00:56:17.370
But you have a grad degree in
film, or you know, television

00:56:17.370 --> 00:56:23.710
or radio, and okay, so,
all right, see that corner

00:56:23.710 --> 00:56:27.520
