sandwich and a glass of lemonade

00:56:34.460 --> 00:56:37.320
and three or four weeks later,
if you're still smiling,

00:56:37.320 --> 00:56:39.730
that's an indication
that you're serious

00:56:39.730 --> 00:56:41.550
